| `RAWG_API_KEY` | [rawg.io/apidocs](https://rawg.io/apidocs) |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` | [console.cloud.google.com](https://console.cloud.google.com) |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` | [console.cloud.google.com](https://console.cloud.google.com) |

